sive uses only such controls are intended to limit use of the companys uranium production to use as fuel for nuclear power plants only and not for use in the production of nuclear weapons rio tinto energy was responsible for  of revenues and  of underlying earnings in  diamonds rio tinto diamondsedit the diavik diamond mine in the northwest territories of canada rio tinto diamonds operates three diamond mines the argyle diamond mine in western australia  ownership the diavik diamond mine in the northwest territories of canada  ownership and the murowa diamond mine located in zimbabwe  ownership together these three mines produce  of the worlds annual production of rough diamonds making rio tinto the worlds thirdlargest producer of mined diamonds the diamond business units most advanced exploration project is the bunder project in district chhatarpur madhya pradesh india where rio tinto became the first foreign group to be granted a prospecting license there rio tinto diamonds generated  of revenues and earnings for rio tinto group in  industrial minerals rio tinto mineralsedit map of dampier salts saltworks in dampier western australia rio tinto minerals is a diverse business group with mining and processing interest in borates salt and gypsum rio tinto borax with main operations in california and another mine in argentina supplies nearly half of the worlds annual demand for refined borates the minerals group is also majority owner of dampier salt which produces over Â million tonnes of salt and Â million tonnes of gypsum annually from its three facilities in northwest australia rio tinto minerals accounted for  of company revenues and contributed  to earnings in  on  january  the management of us borax locked out its hourly workforce replacing the workers with nonunion workers and managers from other rio tinto operations the  international longshore and warehouse union local  members immediately began a fireside vigil that garnered national and international labour